 the CEO dropped on their shareholder letter (images)\n\nFrom the CEO\n- \"there is no comparable in diagnostics'\n\n- \"We now have >500 petabytes of data\" [...] \"In this respect, we stand alone, and our data advantage is only compounding\".\n\nThis is the thesis I shared at my firm, the more data $TEM collects, the bigger and better the moat.\n\nThere's no seconds in the space, $TEM is just THAT GOOD.\n\nWill analysts ever read the shareholder letter and realize $TEM is a one of kind business?\n\n$TEM will literally compound for decades.", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 3, "replyCount": 1, "likeCount": 44, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 4530, "createdAt": "Tue May 05 20:41:05 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 10, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2051764139526332820", "displayTextRange": [0, 281], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "AretardInvestor", "url": "https://x.com/AretardInvestor", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/AretardInvestor", "id": "1927477640442630144", "name": "R\u0336e\u0336t\u0336a\u0336r\u0336d\u0336 Biotech Gambler", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2042690144856346624/6mjQA6Y2_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1927477640442630144/1777817016", "description": "", "location": "NotWallStreet", "followers": 472, "following": 372, "status": "", "canDm": true, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Tue May 27 21:31:16 +0000 2025", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 10001, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 101, "statusesCount": 1810, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": ["2040602023574249529"], "profile_bio": {"description": "BIOTECH ANALYST WORKING FOR PRIVATE FIR