06437"}}, "media_url_https": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HHoXBBdWEAUZC2e.jpg", "original_info": {"focus_rects": [{"h": 730, "w": 1304, "x": 0, "y": 0}, {"h": 1122, "w": 1122, "x": 0, "y": 0}, {"h": 1122, "w": 984, "x": 0, "y": 0}, {"h": 1122, "w": 561, "x": 78, "y": 0}, {"h": 1122, "w": 1304, "x": 0, "y": 0}], "height": 1122, "width": 1304}, "sizes": {"large": {"h": 1122, "w": 1304}}, "type": "photo", "url": "https://t.co/ZnGo10Fe3p"}]}, "card": null, "place": {}, "entities": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [{"indices": [0, 4], "text": "TEM"}], "timestamps": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": []}, "quoted_tweet": null, "retweeted_tweet": null, "isLimitedReply": false, "communityInfo": null, "article": null}], "dropped": [{"reason": "cashtags=12", "tweet": {"type": "tweet", "id": "2052012039766155545", "url": "https://x.com/cevikfinance/status/2052012039766155545", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/cevikfinance/status/2052012039766155545", "text": "$AMD, $ANET, $ALAB, $TEM ve $OSCR bilan\u00e7olar\u0131 genel olarak g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc geldi; $MSTR ise zaten klasik EPS odakl\u0131 de\u011fil.\n\n$AMD: AMD Q1 bilan\u00e7osu tam bir patlama ya\u015fad\u0131: 10.3 milyar dolar gelirle %38 YoY b\u00fcy\u00fcme beklentileri net \u015fekilde a\u015ft\u0131. Veri merkezi geliri art\u0131k toplam\u0131n %50\u2019sinden fazla, EPYC + Instinct AI y\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 ve 6 GW\u2019l\u0131k yeni taahh\u00fctlerle FY rehberini sekt\u00f6r ortalamas\u0131n\u0131n epey \u00fczerine \u00e7\u0131kard\u0131. G\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fc\u015fe g\u00f6re \u201cveri merkezi dominasyonu ger\u00e7ek\u201d, hisse y\u00fckseli\u015fi tamamen hak edilmi\u015f. K\u0131saca a\u00e7\u0131k net: AMD \u015fu an yapay zeka \u00e7ip sekt\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fcn en g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc ikinci oyuncusu.\n\n$MSTR: MSTR bilan\u00e7osu klasik EPS odakl\u0131 de\u011fil, yat\u0131r\u0131mc\u0131lar Bitcoin varl\u0131klar\u0131na ve Michael Saylor\u2019un stratejisine bak\u0131yor. Muhasebe zarar\u0131 \u201cnormie detay\u0131\u201d olarak g\u00f6r\u00fcl\u00fcyor, as\u0131l konu BTC holding miktar\u0131 ve yeni call\u2019lar. Net yorum: Hisse Bitcoin\u2019e inananlar i\u00e7in h\u00e2l\u00e2 \u00e7ok cazip, EPS umursanm\u0131yor. Bitcoin y\u00fckseldik\u00e7e MSTR da y\u00fckselmeye devam eder.\n\n$ANET: ANET %35 gelir b\u00fcy\u00fcmesi ve FY2026 rehber art\u0131\u015f\u0131yla (AI fabric\u2019leri 3.5 milyar dolara \u00e7\u0131kard\u0131) Ethernet\u2019in InfiniBand\u2019i AI networking\u2019de yendi\u011fini bir kez daha kan\u0131tlad\u0131. Ancak marjlar biraz bask\u0131 yaratt\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\u00e7in hisse k\u0131sa vadede d\u00fc\u015f\u00fc\u015f tepkisi verdi. Genel olarak sonu\u00e7lar \u00e7ok sa\u011flam ama piyasa a\u015f\u0131r\u0131 tepki verdi, d\u00fc\u015f\u00fc\u015fler al\u0131m f\u0131rsat\u0131 olmaya devam edecek. Uzun vadede yapay zeka altyap\u0131s\u0131 i\u00e7in h\u00e2l\u00e2 \u00e7ok pozitif.\n\n$TEM: TEM veri ve AI i\u015finde %40 b\u00fcy\u00fcme g\u00f6sterdi, 100 milyon dolar\u0131 a\u015fk\u0131n yeni bookings\u2019le rehberini yukar\u0131 revize etti. K\u0131sa vadede hisse d\u00fc\u015fse de 500 PB veri taban\u0131 moat\u2019\u0131 ve AI kontratlar\u0131 h\u00e2l\u00e2 \u00e7ok g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc. 25%\u2019lik b\u00fcy\u00fcme hikayesi sa\u011flam duruyor. Net: Uzun vadeli yapay zeka veri hikayesine inananlar i\u00e7in dipler al\u0131m f\u0131rsat\u0131 diye d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcn\u00fcyorum.\n\n$ALAB: ALAB %93 YoY gelir patlamas\u0131 ve \u00e7ok g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc Q2 rehberiyle tam bir blowout yapt\u0131, FCF pozitife d\u00f6nd\u00fc. PCIe ve Scorpio ramp\u2019lar\u0131 sorunsuz ilerliyor. A\u00e7\u0131k ve net: ALAB \u015fu anda en temiz AI altyap\u0131 hikayelerinden biri, momentum \u00e7ok g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc. \n\n$OSCR: OSCR rekor d\u00fc\u015f\u00fck MLR (70.5%) ile EPS\u2019te devasa beat (+%75) yapt\u0131 ve net k\u00e2r\u0131 ikiye katlad\u0131. D\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f\u00fcm tamamlanm\u0131\u015f gibi duruyor. \u015eirket yat\u0131r\u0131mc\u0131lar\u0131 i\u00e7in \u201cwe are so back\u201d modu ger\u00e7ek, hisse %12\u2019lik y\u00fckseli\u015f tepkisini tamamen hak etti. Net yorum: Sa\u011fl\u0131k sigortas\u0131nda k\u00e2rl\u0131l\u0131k patlamas\u0131 ger\u00e7ek, OSCR art\u0131k ciddi bir b\u00fcy\u00fcme makinesi.", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 1, "replyCount": 2, "likeCount": 67, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 3929, "createdAt": "Wed May 06 13:06:09 +0000 2026", "lang": "tr", "bookmarkCount": 13, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2052012039766155545", "displayTextRange": [0, 278], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "cevikfinance", "url": "https://x.com/cevikfinance", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/cevikfinance", "id": "938701335456833537", "name": "Cuma Cevik", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1992222532980617216/F4BuYjct_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/938701335456833537/1764112605", "description": "", "location": "Oxford, England", "followers": 30974, "following": 694, "status": "", "canDm": false, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Thu Dec 07 09:26:53 +0000 2017", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 67002, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 2408, "statusesCount": 14188, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": [], "profile_bio": {"description": "Entrepreneur | Trader & Investor | Not Financial Advice", "entities": {"description": {}, "url": {"urls": [{"display_url": "linktr.ee/cumacevik", "expanded_url": "https://linktr.ee/cumacevik", "indices": [0, 23], "url": "https://t.co/Gwn2rrmy6j"}]}}}, "isAutomated": false, "automatedBy": null}, "extendedEntities": {}, "card": null, "place": {}, "entiti